===Adjective===
#(Australian Slang) A term used to describe ''[[faecal matter]]'', used as an alternative to "''[[turd]]''", "brown snake", "chocolate hostage", "coaxial cable", "dropping the kids at the pool", "sewer serpent", "blind mullet".
#:''My mate went to the toilet to punch out a '''nard'''.''
#A flowering plant of the Valerian family that grows in the Himalayas of China, used as a perfume, an incense, a sedative, and an herbal medicine said to fight insomnia, flatulence, birth difficulties, and other minor ailments.